snippet.title: Julián Palacios Gechtman and Skinless Lizard - I Hope To See You Again
snippet.description:
Julián Palacios Gechtman and Skinless Lizard, made from scratch this art.
The full music by Skinless Lizard. 
https://youtu.be/dhut5-8HyBM


Julián Palacios Gechtman Twitter :
https://twitter.com/yulele_palacios

Skinless Lizard Twitter.
https://twitter.com/skinlesslizard


You can find this art on the Virtual Museum " Zium Gallery" only 1GO to download, one of the best retrospective that you can get in your whole life  :

https://theziumsociety.itch.io/the-zium-gallery/download/eyJpZCI6MTMyMzA1MCwiZXhwaXJlcyI6MTY1NDk4NTc3Mn0%3d.1%2bKF4McD4KJd%2baJKSHKvoP7YZ10%3d

This is a journey, in this one I am recognized as " The Specter Of Notalgia", traveling through the places that were most nostalgic in his past life or in his present life he hasn't left yet.

Take the time to explore this museum, the artists are excellent and talented due to the emotions they made me transcribe. (as much paintings as architectures as musics..)
Live this tells a unique and deeply retrospective experience.
The room, the station, the people.

Share this masterpeice of video game to your family, friends and to yourself.

All of this, is just the submerged part of the iceberg of this Virtual Museum.

Enjoy and, good night.
